DataElement.preferredDefinition: The process or condition of being enclosed.:A collection or single item of factual information, derived from measurement or research, from which conclusions may be drawn._A general-purpose markup language for creating special-purpose markup languages. It is capable of describing many different kinds of data. Its primary purpose is to facilitate the sharing of data across different systems, particularly systems connected via the Internet._A placeholder for any XML content.
